
<testpoint> is a unit:
    plural is <testpoints>
    abbreviation is "tp"

<Test Number> is a number:
    valid values:
        0 <testpoints> ... 100 <testpoints>

<Test String> is a string.

<TestEnum> is an enumeration:
    valid values:
        "A";
        "B";
        "C"

<Golden Plan> is a plan:
    during plan:
        <Test Number> = 42 <testpoint>.
        <Test String> = "Hello World".
        <TestEnum> = "A".
        
        show message "Number is " + <Test Number>.
        
        assess <Test Number>:
            1 <testpoint>:
                show message "Single Point".
            41 <testpoints> ... 100 <testpoints>:
                show message "High Value".
            0 <testpoints>:
                show message "Low Value".
            2 <testpoints> ... 40 <testpoints>:
                show message "Low Value".
                
        assess <TestEnum>:
            "A":
                show message "Enum is A".
            "B"; "C":
                show message "Either B or C".
